{"tid":780359,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港搞物業捐血稅有冇得諗？","createTime":"2018-08-15T05:59:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-15T06:28:52.000Z","uid":64694,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"dfe8346933b1a5ee926a1c69513a4b46c7197a75","tid":780359,"uid":64694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T05:59:45.000Z","msg":"班吸血業主平時吸人血就吸得多啦，唔知有冇諗過捐血畀人呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 成日賣廣告話血庫唔夠血叫人去捐血，我覺得搞物業捐血稅可能有得諗<br />\n<br />\n首先呢個稅係以年份計嘅，根據擁有嘅物業嚟計算每年捐血次數，例如有兩個物業就每年捐血兩次，有三個物業就每年捐血三次，如此類推，如果做唔到就要收稅，收嘅稅係該年物業估值嘅10%，以每棟物業嚟計算，除咗可以解決血庫唔夠血嘅問題，重有機會壓抑樓價，令一眾吸血嘅業主可以放返啲血出嚟，唔知有冇得諗呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dd55d8d1cfdd8351d4bc826f554cec44bba9c98","tid":780359,"uid":78304,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T06:01:20.000Z","msg":"將呃綜援班大陸狗全家的去抽血啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4bec4bd6ef3d6d9dfc4d82b32e8c4d0a15471eb","tid":780359,"uid":35696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4dd55d8d1cfdd8351d4bc826f554cec44bba9c98","tid":780359,"uid":78304,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T06:01:20.000Z","msg":"將呃綜援班大陸狗全家的去抽血啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T06:03:56.000Z","msg":"要立 強制勞動法<br />\n冇正職 冇病 又攞綜緩嘅人<br />\n要落公園掃樹葉/守公廁"},{"pid":"a70492cbeda7a1f7e1b1599ef01c35689b26a42c","tid":780359,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4dd55d8d1cfdd8351d4bc826f554cec44bba9c98","tid":780359,"uid":78304,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T06:01:20.000Z","msg":"將呃綜援班大陸狗全家的去抽血啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T06:28:52.000Z","msg":"要啦"}]}